ld be paying $9.00 for a water and a coke, there is no way we would have stopped at the bar. Overall, the hotel is beautiful and the service is good, but you will pay for it; and you will pay BIG. I will not stay here again. There are other high-class hotels that don't rape every cent out of you.	
